    public interface ExtendedInfoProvider<V extends Variable<V,T>,T extends Value<V,T>>
extends InfoProvider<V,T>
    An extension of the InfoProvider class providing extended information. The extended info may be computationally more expensive as it is only computed when needed (see Model.getExtendedInfo(Assignment)).
    Version:
    IFS 1.3 (Iterative Forward Search)
